<h4><strong> Tags </strong></h4>
<h5>A tag is a keyword or label that categorizes your question with other, similar questions. Using the right tags makes it easier for others to find and answer your question.
</h5>
Type to find tags: 
            <div class="inline">
                <input name="authenticity_token" type="hidden" id="authenticity_token" value="<%= form_authenticity_token %>" />
